1.0.name: wordpress/add-edit-delete-listing-for-member-module
1.0.description:
This plugin used for add edit delete and listing module at admin side.Also user can search and sort records. There is also short code implementation for client side.

A few notes about the sections above:

  • romal patel
  • add, edit, delete, listing, searching
  • "3.0" is the lowest version that the plugin will work on
  • "3.4.2" is the highest version that you've successfully used to test the plugin. Note that it might work on higher versions... this is just the highest one you've verified.
